---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
	title='About'
	activePage='About'
	metadata={{
		description: "Hello! I'm Raymond Zhao, and this is all about me as a person.",
		url: "https://raymondzhao.com",
	}}
>
	<div class='w-11/12 mx-auto mt-5'>
		<div class='my-5 rounded-md font-semibold flex'>
			<h1 class="text-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-red-400 to-yellow-600 dark:to-yellow-400 text-transparent bg-clip-text" id="about-me">ABOUT ME</h1>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class='w-11/12 mx-auto mt-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row'>
		<div class='rounded-md md:mr-5 mb-5 md:mb-0 p-5 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800'>
			<img class='rounded-full h-28 w-28 mb-3 object-cover' src='/assets/about.jpg' alt='Raymond Photo' />
			<p>Hello! I'm Raymond, a software developer. I majored in Computer Science and Data Science at the University of Wisconsin-Madison.</p><br />
			<p>
				My first experience with coding was when I was around 8 years old, messing around with JavaScript on Khan Academy. At the beginning of
				my time in high school, I mostly dabbled in competitive programming and Java classes, but after my first year, I started leaning more
				seriously into web development, and as a result, over the last couple of years, I've worked on all sorts of different projects with
				all sorts of people. I'm passionate about making websites that other people will use and enjoy.
			</p><br />
			<p>
				In my free time, I play Magic: the Gathering, work on my programming projects (mostly web development), practice Rubik's Cubes, play
				games, read manga, and cook.
			</p><br />
			<p>Also, the best thing to ever happen to programming is regular expressions. That's just a fact.</p>
			<br />
			<div class='flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center'>
				<img class='h-60' src='/assets/State_Street.jpg' alt='Me with some friends on State Street' />
				<p class='italic md:ml-5'>Me with some friends on State Street at UW-Madison</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class='rounded-md p-5 bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800'>
			<h2 class='text-center font-semibold dark:text-white text-black'>Links</h2>
				<ul class="mt-3 mb-5">
					<li class="flex flex-row items-center">
						<Card name='GitHub' image='/assets/skills/GitHub.png' link='https://github.com/Stinggyray' />
						<h3 class='ml-3 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200'>
							<a href="https://github.com/rl-zhao">GitHub</a>
						</h3>
					</li>
					<li class="flex flex-row items-center">
						<Card name='GitHub' image='/assets/skills/GitHub.png' link='https://github.com/Stinggyray' />
						<h3 class='ml-3 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200'>
							<a href="https://github.com/Stinggyray">GitHub (Personal)</a>
						</h3>
					</li>
					<li class="flex flex-row items-center">
						<Card name='LinkedIn' image='/assets/LinkedIn.png' link='https://www.linkedin.com/in/raymond-l-zhao/' />
						<h3 class='ml-3 text-sm text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200'>
							<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/raymond-l-zhao/">LinkedIn</a>
						</h3>
					</li>
				</ul>
			<h2 class='text-center font-semibold dark:text-white text-black'>Get in touch</h2>
			<div class='flex flex-col'>
				<p class='mb-2'>You can reach me at the following email address (This is the e-mail I check the most often, so you WILL get a response.)</p>
				<a href='mailto:rz@raymondzhao.com' class='text-gray-800 dark:text-yellow-500 underline mb-5'>rz@raymondzhao.com</a>
				<p class="mb-2">This is a backup email address, just in case that one isn't working: (I lose access to this address in 9 months. I don't recommend emailing me here.)</p>
				<a href='mailto:rlzhao@wisc.edu' class='text-gray-800 dark:text-yellow-500 underline'>rlzhao@wisc.edu</a>
			</div>
			<br />
			<p>Here's an up-to-date copy <a href='/assets/Raymond_Zhao_resume.pdf' class='text-gray-800 dark:text-yellow-500 underline'>of my resume</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>

